Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
date-rule-antlr Date parser based on ANTLR
date-rule-combinators Date Rule Interpreter for date descriptions like "next sunday" and "the day before christmas" based on java.time and scala-parser-combinators
date-rule-coco http://ssw.jku.at/Coco/
date-rule-sablecc Some examples to show the use of SableCC
date-rule-javacc Date Parser - evaluating various technologies
date-rule-cup-jflex Date Rule Interpreter for date descriptions like \"next sunday\" and \"the day before christmas\" based on cup and jflex
date-rule-bison Date Parser - evaluating various technologies
date-rule-peg Date Parser - evaluating various technologies
date-rule-parboiled Date Rule Interpreter for date descriptions like "next sunday" and "the day before christmas" based on java.time and parboiled
date-rule-runtime-compile //TODO
date-rule-instaparse Date Rule Interpreter using Instaparse
